{
  "page": "Wayn (guard)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the wagon, see <a href=\"/index.php/Wayn\" title=\"Wayn\">Wayn</a>. For the noble family from the riverlands, see <a href=\"/index.php/House_Wayn\" title=\"House Wayn\">House Wayn</a>. For the noble family from the Vale, see <a href=\"/index.php/House_Waynwood\" title=\"House Waynwood\">House Waynwood</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Wayn</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">Northmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Wayn</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark_guards\" title=\"House Stark guards\">guard</a> sworn to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wayn_(guard)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wayn_(guard)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Wayn is one of the guards, <a href=\"/index.php/Quent\" title=\"Quent\">Quent</a> being the other, who accompany <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Wolfswood\" title=\"Wolfswood\">wolfswood</a> for Bran's first ride since his fall. He and Quent fall behind and then follow <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a> after he spies a turkey, failing to guard Bran, who is seized by <a href=\"/index.php/Wildlings\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wildlings\">wildlings</a>. After the skirmish, Wayn binds <a href=\"/index.php/Osha\" title=\"Osha\">Osha</a> for the return to <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wayn_(guard)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_37\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 37\">Chapter 37</a>, Bran V.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403095634\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.085 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.314 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 385/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10490/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4017/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 196/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 522/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.210/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.52 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  306.017      1 -total\n 86.61%  265.055      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 85.83%  262.661      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.35%   34.742      1 Template:For-multi\n 11.28%   34.523     12 Template:Infobox_value\n 11.10%   33.973      1 Template:Hatnote\n  3.57%   10.910      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.44%    4.400      1 Template:Ref\n  0.86%    2.617      1 Template:Ref/core\n  0.51%    1.547      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:3160-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403095634 and revision id 322415\n -->\n",
